h pull requests or create an issue to start a discussion.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\">What is an awesome list?</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">164.8k</span></span></a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ildoc/awesome-italy-events/blob/master/contributing.md\">Contribution guide</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Available data formats: <a href=\"https://github.com/ildoc/awesome-italy-events/blob/master/data/2021.json\">json</a> - <a href=\"https://github.com/ildoc/awesome-italy-events/blob/master/data/2021.ics\">ics</a></p>\n<p>Editions: <a href=\"https://github.com/ildoc/awesome-italy-events/blob/master/archive/2019.md\">2019</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/ildoc/awesome-italy-events/blob/master/archive/2020.md\">2020</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/ildoc/awesome-italy-events/blob/master/README.md\">2021</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/ildoc/awesome-italy-events/blob/master/2022.md\">2022</a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>Want to add an event? Send a <a href=\"https://github.com/ildoc/awesome-italy-events/blob/master/contributing.md\">pull request</a> or send me a tweet <a href=\"https://twitter.com/il_doc\">@il_doc</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"contents\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contents\" aria-label=\"contents permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45